docs {
  # Confirm Settlement

  Confirm a pending settlement. Only the payee can confirm.

  ## Path Parameters
  - `groupId`: UUID of the group
  - `settlementId`: UUID of the settlement

  ## Response
  Returns confirmed settlement. Balances are updated after confirmation.
}
